Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From a different perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An imposing wall is just a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today we're thinking outside the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find the missing boy from a series of random e-mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.27,0:01:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tsunami-induced shipwreck incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forest fires due to abnormal drought...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And frequently occurring earthquakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet a large meteorite will crash down in the near future or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Feels like Earth is in deep trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, even I, the great detective Mouri Kogorou...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't stop these natural disasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll go ahead and say you normally aren't even capable of stopping a fight among children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:15.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Female High School Detective - Yuki's Casebook
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're taking it slow to be with your family today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:19.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oshibana High School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, after this I need to go investigate the pinball payout rate of the new pachinko parlor nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then a drinking party with the neighborhood association this evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Followed by mahjong at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, I'm so busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, please don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can tell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I'm worried about something!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More like you said so yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:03:01.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,THE PURSUIT OF THE FISH E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, don't tell me some customer dropped this in your shop again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, this is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It be that you've been getting suspicious prank e-mails?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about e-mails all right, but they are not prank ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sender is Osabe Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, a five-year old boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starting about two or three months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He and his father became loyal customers and frequently came to my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently the boy's mother went back to her hometown and hadn't come back since...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since then, he often sent me e-mails via his father's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things like, "I finished all my cucumbers"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I took a bath all by myself"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each day he would report to me his everyday trivial matters like clockwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, why not tell his dad to make the kid stop sending e-mails?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm troubled by his e-mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I got as many as four e-mails from him today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fourâ€”that many?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I'm concerned about the contents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first one goes, "Miss, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm going out with Papa today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"He bought me a chair and a hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Since everyone's wearing one, I'll wear it too."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second one goes, "Since they're getting sweaty and uncomfy, I took off my shoes."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he was doing things that would cause him to sweat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I can see the sign of a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I want to eat a hamburger at your place, Miss."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The third one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A man with black glasses and a woman wearing blue are looking at me, but I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm not gonna cry."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not gonna cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he in some sort of scary situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the fourth one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Will I get caught in the net like that fish and die too?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll die!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, did you e-mail him back, Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked things like "Where are you?" and "What are you doing?"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all the e-mails I got from him didn't seem to be like an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he doesn't know how to open incoming e-mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that kid knows how to send e-mails, but not receive one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he was taught how to send me messages by hitting "reply" which was shown on my e-mail subjects, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's always his dad who checked the inbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, in order to prevent him from opening suspicious e-mails, his dad didn't teach him how.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means, that child's dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is not around him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, he did mention he was hungry in his second e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he's been left alone for that long...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When were the e-mails sent?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's see, the first one came...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 9:07 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second one came at 10:16 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The third one at 11:54 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fourth one came just now, at 3:02 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each e-mail came at longer intervals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is getting tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, speaking of that dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's he doing neglecting his kid like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know about his father, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s family went out on a fishing trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although he did say "the fish got caught in the net" in his e-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one in their right mind would fish around where fishermen are trying to collect their net!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've thought about it too, but the first two messages were both about fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and the people around him are all wearing hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also said his feet were all sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since kids don't usually wear boots in the first place, I bet he was told to put on rubber boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what situation requires wearing a hat, putting on rubber boots, and sitting on a chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, if that was the case, the anglers around him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they did see a kid waiting all by himself for a long time, they should have done something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so caught up in their fishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That they didn't pay attention to that kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're telling you that situation seems odd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then again, I bet that kid has a stiff neck, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, the first e-mail was about how everyone around him are wearing hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second e-mail mentioned a restaurant sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upon sending the third e-mail, Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} saw a man with sunglasses and a woman in blue clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he looking up all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd understand if you put yourself in a child's shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its really a pain, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking as if you were an adult trapped in a kid's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just giving an example...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, could it be that kid's sitting in a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A car?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's not that the kid wanted to look up all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that he couldn't see what's below.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, inside the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was sending e-mails from his seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't be able to see below the waists of the people passing by because the door blocked them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the "people are looking at me" in his third e-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were indeed anglers who were concerned about Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} being left alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They couldn't talk to him from outside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So after they arrived at the fishing spot by car, his dad left and disappeared for whatever reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the kid who had to wait in the car for a long time started sending Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} e-mails to fight boredom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But eventually became tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why hadn't Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this is yesterday's news...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,4 Anglers Currently Missing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the sea is still rough, it's likely accidents are to happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you tried to dial his cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it never went through even though I tried several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's at a place with no signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's been told by his dad to turn the power off after sending e-mails...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To conserve battery power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, have you heard anything about any fishing spot the two of them usually go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, not specifically...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other day, while reading some leisure magazines in my shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His dad suggested that "they should go there".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember that he dog-eared the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six hours have already passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beyond that, I still don't get the meaning of the fourth e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'd get caught in the net like the fish and die"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would a fisherman wander around while keeping a fish in a net?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, normally they'd put it in a cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, why did Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} use that expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found three dog-eared pages!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure it was this magazine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some of my other customers also have the habit of folding a page...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first spot is Nakaarai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second is Kusarazu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the third is Komaezaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all very far away from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's information on recommended inns written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's Saturday, they might have planned to stay for a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:39.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nakaarai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are no reservations made under that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, are there many anglers over there today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although the winds are blowing, it's still a good day for fishing since it's cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it possible the sea got really rough and swallowed some anglers!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you go and jinx it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this a prank call, knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:11:00.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Kusarazu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Osabe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Osabe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one with that name is staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's raining here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On a day like this you can catch lots offish, so many anglers are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know of any accidents because of the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's raining on and off and there isn't any wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:24.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Komaezaki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Osabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know of any guest like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're quite upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, some guests are making a fuss about catching nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On a bright sunny day like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your bait will be too obvious to the fish especially since we have shallow waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no wind, so it's easy to use the rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to catch some fish, hone your goddamn skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} sent me another e-mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and call him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His phone is probably still on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number you have dialed is temporarily\Nnot in service or has been powered off...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what does the e-mail say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I thought there was only one fish, but there were actually three...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I envy those fish..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He thought there was one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has three fish indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mama, why did you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When will you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Papa, have you also left me and gone somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still haven't come back no matter how long I waited...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How I envy those fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I envy those fish"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't make heads or tails of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing we know is that this kid is probably somewhere in one of the three fishing spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakaarai, said to be a good day to fish since it's cloudy, though the winds are blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusarazu, a little bit of drizzle and no wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the third spot is Komaezaki, sunny and without wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then isn't it Nakaarai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where you can catch many?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, you can still catch some in Kusarazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only Komaezaki is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and his dad dog-eared the magazine and decided where they should go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the weather is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Irrelevant, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, even if they say there's no wind, is it possible for them to get no wind at all the entire day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you will if it's sunny and the temperature rises...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, before we hung up, the man in the last inn said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no wind, so it's easy to use the rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Just as I say that, the freaking wind starts blowing though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we assume Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is in the car and keeps looking up all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:22.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then perhaps he's in a daze or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, there's no way for fish to swim up there, like in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fish swimming in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't mention anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look, he e-mailed about seeing three fish instead of one like he originally thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right about that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he's envious after looking at them, doesn't it mean the three fish were swimming together happily?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} seemed pretty lonely ever since his mom went back to her hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he was comparing the three fish to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, where in the world can we find fish swimming in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, maybe he had seen a surreal movie like that with his dad, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, not long ago it was Boys' Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boys' Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May 5th...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the Boys' Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The carp streamers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} can see some carp streamers from where is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since carp streamers will hang down and appear as if they were dead when there's no wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, is it Kusarazu where there's no wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, since he e-mailed about thinking there was one but in fact there were three...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It means there was no wind but it started blowing later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Komaezaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I somehow don't feel well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so hot, and I feel sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hyperthermia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside a sealed car under the scorching sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he stayed still for six hours, it would more than likely happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably already dehydrated by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beyond that, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you already ask the Komaezaki police for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but since there are many fishing spots, it might take long to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only... if only I had consulted with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} much sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, with the sun setting, it might actually be easier to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we can get the whole view of the city from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is the carp streamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention three carps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many people still keep those hanging even though Boys' Day already passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an iconic sight in this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be a big hassle trying to narrow it down to the ones we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome, I've spotted a huge net!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you can catch a whale using that net!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a golf practice course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just surrounded by a huge net so the balls won't fly off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would try and catch a whale with that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} happened to see that net and the carp streamers overlap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he wrote that e-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so we're looking for a golf course that has carp streamers next to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is it, where is it, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it, right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only parking lot where you can see those two overlap is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, this is quite spacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I bet he's here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Search carefully inside every car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, that was written in his e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he's at a place where the carp streamers overlapping with the golf course net...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that signboard can be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's over hereâ€”Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No good, it's locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The miss from Poirot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But papa said I can't leave the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just listen to what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} 1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure feels nice out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from his looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems he's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're going sea-fishing, but the rods are for a river...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also don't see any coolers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s father came here for a different purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, how was that guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy who got caught in the middle of a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did that man who got caught in a fight go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just answer the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it seems his head was bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard an ambulance, so he's probably at a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:19:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was all by myself until this miss and the others came!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I'm sorry, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, you're from Poirot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we saw Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s e-mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried so I came with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell was that, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wanna take this somewhere!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like that, I was knocked out cold and was in a hospital until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Mitsuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a reward for having to wait, I brought you an amazing present!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, his mom looks a lot like Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he e-mailed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So your wife was hospitalized for three months due to tuberculosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want Mitsuru to worry, so I told him she went back to her hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because her TB also made it hard for me to take him for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since today was when they would determine whether she could be discharged or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I would let him see her soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I lied about going fishing and brought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, was I surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since when I came to, I saw my wife looking at me with a worried face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her test results?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satisfactory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't go anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll always be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're back to three as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.87,0:23:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish we could also get back to three soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll settle for being the decorative banner then...
